<th colspan="2" style="text-align:center; font-size:larger;" class="fn summary">Li Bai</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="text-align:center;" class=""><a href="/wiki/File:LiBai.jpg" class="image" title="LiBai.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/4c/LiBai.jpg" width="200" height="343" border="0" /></a><br /></td>
